          "value": "<h3 class=\"framing\">@UUID[Compendium.sfrpg.rules.JaRMioj4isNp7r1P.JournalEntryPage.ZaS9H4rwaFIQTUBC]{Imp Poison}</h3>\n<p><span id=\"ctl00_MainContent_DataListTalentsAll_ctl00_LabelName\"> <strong>Type</strong> poison&nbsp;(injury);<strong> <strong>Save </strong></strong>Fortitude DC 13<strong><strong><br /><strong>Track </strong></strong></strong>Dexterity; <strong><strong><strong><strong>Frequency </strong></strong></strong></strong>1/round for 6 rounds<strong><strong><strong><strong><br /><strong>Cure </strong></strong></strong></strong></strong>1 save</span></p>"
